### Test Tokonomad Backend API
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Create Transaction - Mobile Legends
POST {{baseUrl}}/transactions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "123456789",
  "zoneId": "8888",
  "gameId": "ml",
  "gameName": "Mobile Legends",
  "productId": "ml-1",
  "productName": "86 Diamonds",
  "amount": 20000,
  "paymentMethod": "qris"
}

### 3. Get All Transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions

### 4. Get Transactions by User
GET {{baseUrl}}/transactions?userId=123456789
